Overcast- morning rain- light breeze- baby ducks- turtles.
Light rain just begining as we hoistd anchor and headed to port.   Water still flat calm.  tiny puffs of a breeze.

84 degree air temp. Beautiful day- breezy- heavy boat traffic on lake.  Increased "algae sprigs" in all visible layers of the water- at all three Little Lake Wissota sites.  Algal blooms on surface increased.  Stillson Creek having the most.
